# {{name}}

A Vibe agent app. Written in `.vibe`, compiled to TypeScript, run on the `@vibe/*` runtime.

## Develop
```sh
vibe dev        # watch + recompile main.vibe
vibe check --ts # Vibe + TypeScript diagnostics
vibe build      # emit TypeScript to .vibe/
```

Set `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` in your environment before running the compiled agent.
